title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. tit. 21, Appendices, app 45-B

N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. tit. 21, Appendices, app 45-B
State Regulations
MINISTERIAL ACTS
The purpose of this Appendix is to classify actions or classes
of actions which the issuer has determined to be ministerial actions under this

Part. Ministerial acts include: Any act, decision or commitment required to be made pursuant to
preexisting contractual arrangements by which the issuer is bound. All enforcement actions commenced by or on behalf of the issuer
against third parties to enforce compliance by such third party with any
provision of any contract, law, rule, ordinance, etc. by which such third party
is bound. Notes
